description: This PHP source file manages the display of call signal logs in a web interface, including importing header and footer components, setting up page-specific scripts for fetching and displaying log data dynamically via AJAX, and rendering the HTML structure for logs.

methods.name: document.ready
methods.description: Initializes the page by setting the title and pagination plugin, and executes an AJAX call to fetch call signal logs, which are then displayed in a table.
